    "description": "游戏改编自经典剧目《大鼻子情圣》，短短一小时的流程邀您<strong>以刀剑和头脑</strong>登台对战！<br><br>西哈诺是全法国<strong>最伟大的剑客兼墨客，</strong>而他同样值得称道的还有那全法国<strong>最硕大的鼻子和最火爆的脾气</strong>。<br><br>他曾以一敌百，独自面对一百名士兵也毫无畏惧；他的头脑更是胜过任何在世的诗人。然而，当他陷入对罗克桑娜的苦恋时，却是那样孤立无援——<strong>她又怎么可能爱上这么一个荒唐滑稽的大鼻子呢？</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >而当罗克桑娜心有所属，爱上了一位帅气的年轻士兵时，</h2>西哈诺便发现了一个无需露脸即可表达爱意的大好机会。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/858a9763b79add4d5c86b34c55aabc11.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/858a9763b79add4d5c86b34c55aabc11.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/858a9763b79add4d5c86b34c55aabc11.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >指挥手下的一帮朋友，在回合战中勇敢战斗！</h2>从巴黎到阿拉斯，一路为友谊、为荣誉、为爱情而战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.poster.avif?t=1741359561\" width=600 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.webm?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/37b413383ea5e5528e0b0f90282209d2.mp4?t=1741359561\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >用自己的语言创作情书，赢得罗克桑娜的心！</h2>集齐全套填词卡牌，获得情书灵感，让你诗兴大发！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1750470/extras/fzh-cn-victory.jpg?t=1741359561\" /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在这个舞台上，你是诗人，是爱人，是朋友，也是战士。</h2>在有史以来最伟大的戏剧之中，站上舞台中心！<br>